{"tid":198425,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"emilia做過d乜要比你地幸災樂禍？","createTime":"2017-04-12T13:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T01:21:33.000Z","uid":6327,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3448b07328c2fd0431d2c4544e06f55755f3eed5","tid":198425,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"其實你班人係咪有問題？<br />\n<br />\n個枕頭公仔比狗屌 人地平時做過d咩陰質野？<br />\n點解可以無啦啦話人扺撚死？<br />\n更荒謬嘅係<br />\n原因就係因為佢「Re0」嘅女主角。<br />\n<br />\n我肯定如果個角色係只係一個普通人<br />\n比狗屌唔會有咁多無人性嘅回應<br />\n<br />\n隻狗屌完就真係完結 翻唔到轉頭<br />\n人地一家已經夠傷心<br />\n你仲要踩多兩腳 <br />\n抵撚死啊 邊個叫你做雞<br />\n<br />\n你班人仲係人黎？<br />\n到底係咪連登仔淨係識食花生<br />\n定係根本連人最基本嘅惻隱之心都無？<br />\n<br />\n覺得無問題嘅，<br />\n你當我同現代社會脫撚左節算啦"},{"pid":"de30cd6331eceedd322a917febc236252f799ad5","tid":198425,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42563c62d60540d6698c7bb1cbdc56ba1879b876","tid":198425,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DJ410S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DJ410S.jpg&h=2e1d50d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e57111408a8c8cb782f7e55fda29a50f201422f","tid":198425,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"積翻d口德啦"},{"pid":"aa6c697d7faf7f83940f05322b1978f6de132b32","tid":198425,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積翻d口德啦</blockquote><br />\n邊到可以換禮品?"},{"pid":"8ebdca3657605aea79aac28572d22a6880ae025d","tid":198425,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DJ410S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DJ410S.jpg&h=2e1d50d9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockq